      "description": "Hey friends! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in solid shape and has plenty of life left for all your road trips and grocery runs! It runs super smooth and has been well-loved. If you're looking for something reliable that still looks great on the road, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
