    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and comfort for its next owner. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only minor road peppering on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has been kept strictly smoke-free; the premium upholstery shows minimal bolster wear, and all interior electronics\u2014including the dual-zone climate control, navigation, and heated seats\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, having recently undergone a full multi-point inspection, oil change, and brake pad replacement. The engine pulls smoothly with no hesitation, and the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable. It has been garage-kept, features a clean title, and comes with a documented service history. This is a dependable, well-cared-for example that is ready for the road today.",
